name: DyFSO-MAS
short_description: we propose a decentralized platform for dynamic  Web services orchestration based MAS, called DyFSO-MAS (Dynamic Framework System Orchestration Multi Agent System). This platform can orchestrate web services by compositional logic provided by distributed agents (local or remote).
